/** * A dataset containing one or more data series containing (x, y) data items, * where all series in the dataset share the same set of x-values. This is a * restricted form of the {@link XYDataset} interface (which allows independent * x-values between series). This is used primarily by the * {@link org.jfree.chart.renderer.xy.StackedXYAreaRenderer}. */
